name: Why have I googled it up?
name_original: Why have I googled it up?
description:
This is the entry for "20 Second Game Jam".

You are a white collar who whatches too many unrelated things at work.
The boss is coming and you don't want to get caught, do you?
Try your best and close all tabs or else you will be fired!

P.S.: we want to know how many attempts you had,
write down in comments :D
